quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  15,80,Abotan no mu foͻ no nso anye asomafoͻ no anni
  15,81,"Yε’de Yεn’sεnkyerεnee nso maa wͻn, nanso wͻ’danee wͻn ho frii ho"
  15,82,Na wͻ’dwidwa (anaasε wͻ’bͻne) mmepͻ no mu deyε afie anaasε atenaeε wͻ abodweε mu
  15,83,Nanso asotwee no too wͻn anͻpa tutuutu
  15,84,Deε wͻnsa kaeε no ho amma mfasoͻ amma wͻn
  15,85,"Yε’de nokorε na εbͻͻ ͻsoro ne asaase ne deε εwͻ ne mmienu mfinfii no. Nokorε sε Dͻnhwere no reba, enti (Nkͻmhyεni), bu w’ani gu (ͻhaw ne ateeteε a boniayεfoͻ no de redi mo no) so wͻ ahummͻborͻ ne bͻne fafri mu"
  15,86,"Nokorε sε, wo Wura Nyankopͻn ne Ɔbͻͻ adeε no, Ɔne Onimdefo no"
  15,87,Ampa sε Y’ama wo ‘Sab’al Masaani’ Nsεm pͻ nson a yεtaa kenkan de bͻ Nyankopͻn abodin εna Qur’aan Kεseε no
  15,88,"Na hwε na w’anyε aniwᴐmu wͻ deε Yε’de ama wͻn mu (nnipa) sononko-sononko no ho, na εmma wowerε nso nnho wͻ wͻn ho, na brε wataban ase fama agyidiefoͻ no"
  15,89,"Na ka sε: “Nokorε sε, medeε meyε kͻkͻbͻni pefee"
  15,90,Sεdeε Yε’siane demaa akuo-akuo no
  15,91,"Wͻn a wͻ’akyekyε Akenkan Nwoma no mu, (gye εfa baabi die na wͻ’nnye baabi nnie) no"
  15,92,"Enti (Nkͻmhyεni), Mede wo Wura Nyankopͻn di nse sε, nokorε Yε’bebisa wͻn nyinaa"
  15,93,Wͻ dwuma a na wͻ’die no ho asεm
  15,94,"Enti pae mu ka deε yahyε woͻ no, na twe woho fri abosomsomfoͻ no ho"
  15,95,"Nokorε sε, Yεsom bo ma wo wͻ afεwdifoͻ no ho"
  15,96,"Wͻn a wͻ’ayε anyame foforͻ aka Nyankopͻn ho no, εnkyε koraa wͻ’behunu"
  15,97,"Ampa sε, Ye’nim yie sεdeε wͻ’rekeka no si fa ha wo wͻ w’akoma mu"
  15,98,"Enti wodeε bᴐ wo Wura Nyankopͻn abodin na kamfo no, na ka wͻn a wͻ’de wͻn anim butu fͻm no ho"
  15,99,Na som wo Wura Nyankopͻn kͻpem sε (deε εda biribiara adi) pefee no bεba wo soͻ